No. 55/4/CF-66(1)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRET ARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 10th November l966.
The undersigned is directed to state that
Shri Gulzarilal Nanda relinquished the office of Minister
of Home Affairs with effect from the afternoon of November 9
1966.
The Prime Minister has assumed the office of
Minister of Home Affairs in addition to her present duties.
(D.P. Chopra)
for Cabinet Secretary.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
All Parliamentary Secretaries.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the Prime Minister/the
Joint,Secretary to the Prime Minister/the Private Secretary
to the Prime Minister, for information.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/the
Private Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Go ver nment of India/Chai rman,

Government of India/Lok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha

( D.P. Chop ra )
